First download original Bodmer's TFT_eSPI library: https://github.com/Bodmer/TFT_eSPI

If you are using ST7735 driver tft display:
In User_Setup comment out all display drivers (or just replace if with file from this folder)
In User_Setup_Select uncomment #include <User_Setups/Setup2_ST7735.h> this line and comment out all other drivers (or just replace if with file from this folder)
Replace Setup2_ST7735.h file in User_Setups with file from this folder
Copy and paste Segoe_UI font files to Fonts/GFXFF (not all fonts are used in code)
Replace gfxfont.h file in Fonts/GFXFF
